{"tid":534571,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"英國Mous推岀地表最強防撞保護套，可以防子彈！","createTime":"2018-01-20T03:06:33.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-20T06:21:14.000Z","uid":28366,"like":8,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"cbb6636bf0301707dcb8572c5507ebc5ec896d8b","tid":534571,"uid":28366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-20T03:06:33.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=je5U2l90J3A\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dje5U2l90J3A&d=uZLgPutlfvzOgorFboHIZ3Iou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=9bc431c6\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=je5U2l90J3A</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>iPhone</strong> 即使一直用上金屬機身，但始終難以抵禦從高處墜下時，所能產生的衝擊力，輕則機身凹陷，重則可以令到螢幕破裂甚至連內裡的顯示螢幕都損壞。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://searchingc.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/%E8%8B%B1%E5%9C%8B-Mous-%E5%9C%B0%E8%A1%A8%E6%9C%80%E5%BC%B7%E9%98%B2%E6%92%9E%E4%BF%9D%E8%AD%B7%E5%A5%9726.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fsearchingc.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F02%2F%25E8%258B%25B1%25E5%259C%258B-Mous-%25E5%259C%25B0%25E8%25A1%25A8%25E6%259C%2580%25E5%25BC%25B7%25E9%2598%25B2%25E6%2592%259E%25E4%25BF%259D%25E8%25AD%25B7%25E5%25A5%259726.jpg&h=7fd47925&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>Mous</strong> 的 <strong>iPhone</strong> 保護套，卻可以讓 <strong>iPhone</strong> 從 <strong>45 呎</strong>（<strong>13.7 米</strong>）約 <strong>4.5 層</strong>高的地方，讓 <strong>iPhone</strong> 以自由落體的墜地而絲毫無損。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://searchingc.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/image1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fsearchingc.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F02%2Fimage1.jpg&h=328d1491&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n這個手機套的厚度就只有 <strong>2.7mm</strong>，研發團隊表示他們利用了革命性的氣袋式結構新技術 <strong>Airo Shock</strong>，加入到這個手機套之中。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://searchingc.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/CyCANkiWgAAmmEX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fsearchingc.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F02%2FCyCANkiWgAAmmEX.jpg&h=2060afc5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n他們把氣袋結構造成了細微的氣泡，在手機套之中形成了一習彈簧結構，在不增加體積之下，可以吸收巨大的衝擊力。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://searchingc.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/mous-iphone-7-wood-base-720x480-c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fsearchingc.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F02%2Fmous-iphone-7-wood-base-720x480-c.jpg&h=3b859ab7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n用戶亦可以另行選擇手機套背面的物料，例如是雲石、皮革、甚至是碳纖紋物料。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">原黑皮款</span><br />\n<img src=\"http://searchingc.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/%E8%8B%B1%E5%9C%8B-Mous-%E5%9C%B0%E8%A1%A8%E6%9C%80%E5%BC%B7%E9%98%B2%E6%92%9E%E4%BF%9D%E8%AD%B7%E5%A5%9705.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fsearchingc.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F02%2F%25E8%258B%25B1%25E5%259C%258B-Mous-%25E5%259C%25B0%25E8%25A1%25A8%25E6%259C%2580%25E5%25BC%25B7%25E9%2598%25B2%25E6%2592%259E%25E4%25BF%259D%25E8%25AD%25B7%25E5%25A5%259705.jpg&h=dfad5640&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">核桃木款 </span><br />\n<img src=\"http://searchingc.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/%E8%8B%B1%E5%9C%8B-Mous-%E5%9C%B0%E8%A1%A8%E6%9C%80%E5%BC%B7%E9%98%B2%E6%92%9E%E4%BF%9D%E8%AD%B7%E5%A5%9720.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fsearchingc.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F02%2F%25E8%258B%25B1%25E5%259C%258B-Mous-%25E5%259C%25B0%25E8%25A1%25A8%25E6%259C%2580%25E5%25BC%25B7%25E9%2598%25B2%25E6%2592%259E%25E4%25BF%259D%25E8%25AD%25B7%25E5%25A5%259720.jpg&h=b9bb70a2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">竹木紋款</span><br />\n<img src=\"http://searchingc.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/%E8%8B%B1%E5%9C%8B-Mous-%E5%9C%B0%E8%A1%A8%E6%9C%80%E5%BC%B7%E9%98%B2%E6%92%9E%E4%BF%9D%E8%AD%B7%E5%A5%9703.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fsearchingc.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F02%2F%25E8%258B%25B1%25E5%259C%258B-Mous-%25E5%259C%25B0%25E8%25A1%25A8%25E6%259C%2580%25E5%25BC%25B7%25E9%2598%25B2%25E6%2592%259E%25E4%25BF%259D%25E8%25AD%25B7%25E5%25A5%259703.jpg&h=19c25fc7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">碳纖紋款</span><br />\n<img src=\"http://searchingc.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/%E8%8B%B1%E5%9C%8B-Mous-%E5%9C%B0%E8%A1%A8%E6%9C%80%E5%BC%B7%E9%98%B2%E6%92%9E%E4%BF%9D%E8%AD%B7%E5%A5%9716.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fsearchingc.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F02%2F%25E8%258B%25B1%25E5%259C%258B-Mous-%25E5%259C%25B0%25E8%25A1%25A8%25E6%259C%2580%25E5%25BC%25B7%25E9%2598%25B2%25E6%2592%259E%25E4%25BF%259D%25E8%25AD%25B7%25E5%25A5%259716.jpg&h=465945e0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">白貝母款</span><br />\n<img src=\"http://searchingc.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/2595553.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fsearchingc.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F11%2F2595553.jpeg&h=b8ff72cb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n同時手機套的底部設計上，作出了可以同時迎合<strong> iPhone</strong>的設計。<br />\n<img src=\"http://searchingc.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/%E8%8B%B1%E5%9C%8B-Mous-%E5%9C%B0%E8%A1%A8%E6%9C%80%E5%BC%B7%E9%98%B2%E6%92%9E%E4%BF%9D%E8%AD%B7%E5%A5%9725.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fsearchingc.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F02%2F%25E8%258B%25B1%25E5%259C%258B-Mous-%25E5%259C%25B0%25E8%25A1%25A8%25E6%259C%2580%25E5%25BC%25B7%25E9%2598%25B2%25E6%2592%259E%25E4%25BF%259D%25E8%25AD%25B7%25E5%25A5%259725.jpg&h=f15b7ec6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://searchingc.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/%E8%8B%B1%E5%9C%8B-Mous-%E5%9C%B0%E8%A1%A8%E6%9C%80%E5%BC%B7%E9%98%B2%E6%92%9E%E4%BF%9D%E8%AD%B7%E5%A5%9724.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fsearchingc.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F02%2F%25E8%258B%25B1%25E5%259C%258B-Mous-%25E5%259C%25B0%25E8%25A1%25A8%25E6%259C%2580%25E5%25BC%25B7%25E9%2598%25B2%25E6%2592%259E%25E4%25BF%259D%25E8%25AD%25B7%25E5%25A5%259724.jpg&h=3df17e58&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n預購期間更會附送一個可以在牆身上吸附式固定手機的小配件 One-Touch Mount。<br />\n<img src=\"http://searchingc.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/%E8%8B%B1%E5%9C%8B-Mous-%E5%9C%B0%E8%A1%A8%E6%9C%80%E5%BC%B7%E9%98%B2%E6%92%9E%E4%BF%9D%E8%AD%B7%E5%A5%9718.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fsearchingc.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F02%2F%25E8%258B%25B1%25E5%259C%258B-Mous-%25E5%259C%25B0%25E8%25A1%25A8%25E6%259C%2580%25E5%25BC%25B7%25E9%2598%25B2%25E6%2592%259E%25E4%25BF%259D%25E8%25AD%25B7%25E5%25A5%259718.jpg&h=53d357d2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://searchingc.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/%E8%8B%B1%E5%9C%8B-Mous-%E5%9C%B0%E8%A1%A8%E6%9C%80%E5%BC%B7%E9%98%B2%E6%92%9E%E4%BF%9D%E8%AD%B7%E5%A5%9715.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fsearchingc.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F02%2F%25E8%258B%25B1%25E5%259C%258B-Mous-%25E5%259C%25B0%25E8%25A1%25A8%25E6%259C%2580%25E5%25BC%25B7%25E9%2598%25B2%25E6%2592%259E%25E4%25BF%259D%25E8%25AD%25B7%25E5%25A5%259715.jpg&h=c8d64203&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://searchingc.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/%E8%8B%B1%E5%9C%8B-Mous-%E5%9C%B0%E8%A1%A8%E6%9C%80%E5%BC%B7%E9%98%B2%E6%92%9E%E4%BF%9D%E8%AD%B7%E5%A5%9713.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fsearchingc.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F02%2F%25E8%258B%25B1%25E5%259C%258B-Mous-%25E5%259C%25B0%25E8%25A1%25A8%25E6%259C%2580%25E5%25BC%25B7%25E9%2598%25B2%25E6%2592%259E%25E4%25BF%259D%25E8%25AD%25B7%25E5%25A5%259713.jpg&h=0eb94b84&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">海外媒體推介</span><br />\n<img src=\"http://searchingc.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/Screen-Shot-2017-02-21-at-9.08.20-PM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fsearchingc.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F02%2FScreen-Shot-2017-02-21-at-9.08.20-PM.jpg&h=0c934522&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n適合iPhone X / 8 使用<br />\n讓 iPhone 以自由落體的墜地而絲毫無損<br />\n氣袋式結構新技術 Airo Shock<br />\n彈簧結構可以吸收巨大的衝擊力<br />\n多款時尚美觀款式選擇，例如是大理石、皮革、木、甚至是作用碳纖紋物料<br />\n厚度只有 2.7mm<br />\n重量：42g<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://searchingc.com/collections/mousx8-nmg/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fsearchingc.com%2Fcollections%2Fmousx8-nmg%2F&d=uZLgPutlfvzOgorFboHIZ3Iou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=c25f65c0\" target=\"_blank\">http://searchingc.com/collections/mousx8-nmg/</a>"},{"pid":"55ca3708aa684440b31ab2917afb1d8c36d4e435","tid":534571,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-20T03:08:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee2332f9aaeb494650358545f8ead998baf1f808","tid":534571,"uid":28366,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-20T03:08:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2884960485dc80be81b6f6b3ecad146967b87c53","tid":534571,"uid":48631,"like":28,"dislike":3,"score":25,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-20T03:10:22.000Z","msg":"屌,以為講緊condom<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23c635c516ed5cbe4d820414d45a1e0902744a42","tid":534571,"uid":51904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-20T03:11:16.000Z","msg":"咁你放係心口搵人開槍試下"},{"pid":"c0cae595d0d1554d75b208394343a979285668e3","tid":534571,"uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-20T03:11:20.000Z","msg":"香港有無人買過實測?"},{"pid":"c2c34f72079cd205ddd867c1c3d4f45aafd4c410","tid":534571,"uid":28366,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"c0cae595d0d1554d75b208394343a979285668e3","tid":534571,"uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-20T03:11:20.000Z","msg":"香港有無人買過實測?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-20T03:12:17.000Z","msg":"買咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa9462a583d2b65f50e27d297ab0f20601911